Now here is where it gets spicy,  "How do you avoid duplicate processing in a consumer?

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:14,447
Enable enable.auto.commit=false, process the batch, then call commitSync().

3
00:00:14,447 --> 00:00:25,934
Wrap the external side effect (e.g., database write) and the commit in an idempotent design so re-processing the same record has no net effect.

